lead_paragraph: At least 14 civilians were killed and dozens were wounded after the Islamist militants struck the Lido beachfront restaurant in Somalia’s capital.

byline.contributor: Mohammed Ibrahim reported from Mogadishu, and Jeffrey Gettleman from Nairobi, Kenya.
byline.original: By MOHAMMED IBRAHIM and JEFFREY GETTLEMAN

headline.main: Shabab Stage Deadly Attack on Beachfront Restaurant in Mogadishu

snippet: At least 14 civilians were killed and dozens were wounded after the Islamist militants struck the Lido beachfront restaurant in Somalia’s capital.
abstract: Somali officials say at least 14 civilians were killed and dozens wounded after Shabab militants attacked beachside restaurant in Mogadishu.
